    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create a seal on the target that allows it to be summoned with the Kuchiyose: Shunkoku Kasei (p180) technique at a range of 3 miles. This technique costs 2 Chakra, plus half the target's level or HD (minimum 8 total Chakra).</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The second and fourth step increase the range by 1 mile and the duration by 1 day.<br><br>The fifth step requires ECL 18 to learn, and allows you to create a scroll when performing this technique.<br><br>The scroll costs 4 Chakra, requires a Fuinjutsu check (DC 23) and 30 minutes to make. The scroll lasts until used, or until this technique's duration expires. The scroll can be used to perform Shunkoku Kasei as an attack action, without paying Chakra or making a Perform check.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
